In [161]:
def error(model_first, model_second, time):
    t_index_first = int(time / model_first.params['data_dt'])
    size_first = len(model_first.phi[t_index_first])
    f_first = interpolate.interp1d(
        np.arange(size_first) * model_first.params['data_dx'],
        model_first.phi[t_index_first]
    )
    t_index_second = int(time / model_second.params['data_dt'])
    size_second = len(model_second.phi[t_index_second])
    f_second = interpolate.interp1d(
        np.arange(size_second) * model_second.params['data_dx'],
        model_second.phi[t_index_second]
    )
    dx = min(model_first.params['data_dx'], model_second.params['data_dx'])
    result = 0.0
    for i in range(max(size_first, size_second)):
        if i * dx > (size_first - 1) * model_first.params['data_dx']:
            break
        if i * dx > (size_second - 1) * model_second.params['data_dx']:
            break
        result += (f_first(i * dx) - f_second(i * dx)) ** 2
    result = np.sqrt(result) / model_first.params['width']
    return result
